<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html" charset="UTF-8"/>
    <title>머스테치 실습3</title>
</head>
<body>
<h2>머스테치 표현 형식</h2>

Data 객체 <br>
{{ standardDate }}<br>
LocalDate 객체<br>
{{ localDate }}<br>
LocalDateTime 객체<br>
{{ localDateTime }}<br>
<br>

Member 클래스 객체<br>
{{# member }}
    {{ id }} <br>
    {{ username }} <br>
    {{ password }} <br>
    {{ joinDate }} <br>
    <span id="joinDateTime">{{ joinDateTime }}</span> <br>
{{/ member }}

<br>

숫자 형식 세자리 수마다 콤마 <br>
<span id="numberFormat1">{{ number1 }}</span> <br>
숫자 형식 세자리 수마다 콤마 + 원 표기 <br>
<span id="numberFormat2">{{ number1 }}</span>원 <br>
숫자 형식 소숫점 2자리에서 반올림 <br>
<span id="numberFormat3">{{ number2 }}</span> <br>

    <script>
        window.onload = function(){
            let dateText  = document.getElementById("joinDateTime").innerText;
            console.log( dateText );
            //2022-11-27T21:56:31.692810800

            const dateObj = new Date( dateText );
            const year = dateObj.getFullYear();
            const month = dateObj.getMonth() + 1;
            const date = dateObj.getDate();
            const hour = dateObj.getHours();
            const min = dateObj.getMinutes();
            const sec = dateObj.getSeconds();
            let dateFormat = year + '-' + month + '-' + date + ' ' +
                             hour + ':' + min + ':' + sec;
            document.getElementById("joinDateTime").innerText = dateFormat;

            let numberText1  = document.getElementById("numberFormat1").innerText;
            let result1 = Number( numberText1 ).toLocaleString();
            document.getElementById("numberFormat1").innerText = result1;

            let numberText2  = document.getElementById("numberFormat2").innerText;
            let result2 = Number( numberText2 ).toLocaleString();
            document.getElementById("numberFormat2").innerText = result2;

            let numberText3  = document.getElementById("numberFormat3").innerText;
            const result3 = ((Number(numberText3)).toFixed(2));
            document.getElementById("numberFormat3").innerText = result3;

        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>
